tps://www.nme.com/news/music/hugh-jackman-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-get-tickets-3808633">休·杰克曼 (Hugh Jackman</a> ) 之前均已确认成为 BST 头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3809226">之后</a>第五位加入明年阵容的艺人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">《红衣女孩》</a>将提供支持，更多演出将在未来几周内公布。门票于本周五（11 月 15 日）上午 9 点（格林威治标准时间）开始公开发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Famerican-express-presents-bst-hyde-park-tickets%2Fartist%2F1842565%23concerts" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。</p><p>随着罗德里戈宣布明年将成为格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的头条新闻，并于同一个周末在海德公园成为头条新闻，猜测将会增加。 </p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_olivia_bst_2000x1270.jpg" /></p><p>在周一（6 月 30 日）在曼彻斯特的 Co-op Live Arena 表演之前，她还有 6 月 28 日和 29 日的免费时段。</p><p>她<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/olivia-rodrigo-live-at-glastonbury-2022-lily-allen-3255786">曾在 2022 年吸引了大批观众来到 The Other Stage</a> ，而罗德里戈<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153">已经是博彩公司最有希望登上 2025 年金字塔舞台的热门人选之一</a>。</p><p>其他传闻中的头条人物包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日乐队 (Green Day)</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cher">雪儿 (Cher)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-reportedly-in-talks-for-legends-slot-at-glastonbury-2025-3790138">正在就接手令人垂涎的传奇席位进行“有意义的谈判”</a> ，今年该职位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shania-twain-talks-glastonbury-2024-legends-slot-honour-of-my-life-3600979">由仙妮亚·唐恩 (Shania Twain) 接任</a>。</p><p> Worthy Farm bash 的门票<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">本周开始发售，</a>长途汽车和套票将于周四（11 月 14 日）下午 6 点（格林威治标准时间）发售，标准票将于周日（11 月 17 日）上午 9 点（格林威治标准时间）发售。门票将<a href="https://glastonbury.seetickets.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>独家发售。</p><p>去年的 BST 海德公园演出阵容包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-stevie-nicks-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-3765318">Stevie Nicks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-london-stage-times-3774511">Kylie Minogue</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/special-guests-announced-for-stray-kids-london-bst-hyde-park-show-3763729">Stray Kids</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-sza-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-3760887">SZA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/more-support-acts-added-to-kings-of-leons-london-bst-hyde-park-2024-show-3762832">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3598527">Morgan Wallen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3763248">Andrea Bocelli</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3553493">Robbie Williams</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-shania-twain-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3764110">Shania Twain</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，罗德里戈最近从<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/tiktok">TikTok</a>中删除了一首被<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>竞选团队使用的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-removes-song-from-tiktok-after-its-use-by-trump-campaign-3811207">歌曲</a>。</p><p>这位歌手一直是一位直言不讳的生殖权利活动家，今年早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-launches-reproductive-rights-initiative-the-fund-4-good-3592805">宣布启动 The Fund 4 Good 倡议，</a>作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-2024-guts-world-tour-shows-buy-tickets-3497458">“Guts”世界巡演</a>的一部分。</p><p>正如她在二月份解释的那样，该组织致力于“支持所有妇女、女孩和寻求生殖健康自由的人”，并将“直接支持社区非营利组织，这些非营利组织倡导女孩教育、支持生殖权利和防止基于性别的性别歧视”。暴力。”</p><p>在她的职业生涯中，罗德里戈一直是生殖权利的坚定支持者，这位歌手表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-speaks-out-over-abortion-rights-our-bodies-should-never-be-in-the-hands-of-politicians-3218888">，她对最高法院在 2022 年推翻罗伊诉韦德案的决定感到“心碎”</a> 。</p><p>在选举前，罗德里戈还基于特朗普的竞争对手<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡马拉·哈里斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-throws-support-behind-kamala-harris-over-reproductive-rights-stance-3777706">在生殖权利方面的立场，支持了她</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-announces-her-biggest-ever-uk-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-3811479">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 宣布她在 BST 海德公园 (BST Hyde Park 2025) 举行的有史以来规模最大的英国演出的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
